Version 0.9.10
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Released: 2026-07-xx

Note:
This release features a lot of new stuff, the most noticeable are the modular overview page, shareable school configs, the new mobile view and just polishing.

Features:
 * Background sync
 * Added notifications for scheduled exams and new grades
 * Error dialog, just in case
 * Scrollable calendar on the schedule page
 * Navigation overhaul with handy mobile view
 * Preferences: now it's possible to change app settings
 * School config: share non-standard configurations with your friends
 * Overview: new, completely modular and adaptive for different schools

Misc:
 * More reliable caching, its loading and cleaning on logout
 * Initial LUDUS API implementation
 * Enforced HTTPS
 * Bearer token leaking prevention
 * Added Danish, Russian and Ukrainian translations

